OL,3,CThames Water to axe 140 jobs in bid
OL,4,Cto 'strengthen financial resilience'
OL,6,FThames Water has announced plans to
OL,7,Fcut more than 100 jobs in a bid to
OL,8,Fhelp strengthen its "financial
OL,9,Fresilience".
OL,11,FThe company told the GMB Union of its
OL,12,Fplans at a meeting today which will
OL,13,Finvolve the loss of retail and
OL,14,Fdigital jobs.
OL,16,FThe GMB said Thames Water told the
OL,17,Funion at a meeting on Thursday that
OL,18,Fit is to start consulting on up to
OL,19,F140 redundancies.
